relation: I am at day camp all summer as a counselor in training, so I haven’t been home to really… well, draw. However, I do some things in Arts and Crafts, and today we did balloon-people. I however, took a different take. Made with: a red balloon, red, yellow and purple construction paper, and puffballs/feathers for the birdy. :3
I made a chimera's mouth out of sand. xD
